        "action": "Review transparency around additional charges to mortgages",
        "additional_details": "We feel these charges can push borrowers into debt or repossession.",
        "background": "We urge the UK Government to review the transparency of how legal fees are charged by mortgage lenders for accounts in arrears. We demand itemised charges, a cap on legal costs, a free dispute process, and an inquiry into past unfair repossessions.",
